data.description: Welcome to this adorable 5-bedroom, 3-full-bath gem nestled in Pennington Place. Boasting an open floor plan, this home invites you in with a spacious family room featuring cathedral ceilings and a striking stack stone fireplace. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering ample space, a walk-in closet, and a recently remodeled bathroom that includes a separate soaking tub and shower. The downstairs features a secondary bedroom with a bathroom. Upstairs, discover three additional bedrooms along with another full bath. The thoughtful design extends to the outdoors, where you'll find a new fenced yard, offering privacy and a perfect space for relaxation or entertaining.
